{"questionId":"22707279","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The displacement of the T-shirt, <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi></math> seconds after it is launched, is given by the vector equation</p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>29</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn><mo> </mo><mfenced><mrow><mi>cos</mi><mo> </mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow></mfenced><mo> </mo><mi>t</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>29</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn><mo> </mo><mfenced><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mi>θ</mi></mrow></mfenced><mo> </mo><mi>t</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>9</mn><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math></p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Hence find the maximum possible value for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math> if there was no seating to block the path of the T-shirt.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>valid method to find maximum (e.g. sketch graph, find derivative)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>maximum value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math> is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>88</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong><br>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>(M1)A0</strong></em> for an unsupported answer of “<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>45</mn></math>” or <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>785398</mn><mo>…</mo></mrow></mfenced></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"22707279","r